name: Garrick Albert
description: Passionate, honest, introverted, warmhearted, down-to-earth. Night owl. Enjoy intense, intelligent conversations; have a dry, sometimes offbeat, often mischievous sense of humor. Reserved on the outside, goth at heart. Music makes me feel alive, nature gives me peace. Special place in my heart for books and dogs. In true Aquarian style I tend to march to the beat of my own drum,I like to play piano
